Last updated: December 2025

SoundFocus respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how your information is handled when you use the SoundFocus app.

1. No Personal Data Collection

SoundFocus does not collect, store, or process any personal data.
We do not require you to create an account, sign in, or provide any personal information.

2. No Internet Connection Required

SoundFocus works fully offline. All features, including focus sessions, statistics, and sounds, function without any internet connection.

3. Local Data Storage Only

All usage data such as:
	•	Completed focus sessions
	•	Total focus time
	•	Focus score
are stored locally on your device only using secure local storage. This data is never transmitted to any server or third party.

4. No Ads & No Tracking

SoundFocus contains:
	•	No advertisements
	•	No analytics tools
	•	No tracking systems
	•	No third-party SDKs that collect user data

5. Children’s Privacy

SoundFocus does not knowingly collect any data from children under the age of 13. Since no data is collected at all, it is safe for all age groups.

6. Data Security

Because all data is stored locally on your device and never transmitted, your data remains fully under your control.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

If this Privacy Policy is updated, the new version will be published within the app or on the official App Store page.

8. Contact

If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, you may contact us via the support email provided on the App Store page.

6353ww@gmail.com
